els Good]]''\n|\n* Released: 23 October 2015\n* Label: Capitol\n* Format: CD, DL, [[LP album|LP]], streaming\n| 1 || 2 || 1 || 3 || 12 || 1 || 1 || 2 || 1 || 1\n|\n* US: 496,000<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/list/7356755/billboard-top-40-money-makers-rich-list|title=Taylor Swift Tops Billboard's Top Money-Makers List of 2015|author=Billboard Staff|website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]]|date=May 5, 2016|accessdate=May 8, 2016}}</ref>\n* WW: 1,000,000<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barilla|first1=Lucille|title=Five Seconds Of Summer Hit One Million Sales Worldwide With 'Sounds Good, Feels Good' Album|url=http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2016/04/07/five-seconds-of-summer-hit-one-million|website=StarPulse.com|publisher=Lucille Barilla|accessdate=29 May 2016}}</ref>\n| <!-- Add sales only with a reliable source (not twitter accounts)-->\n* BPI: Gold<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n*IRMA: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Youngblood (5 Seconds of Summer album)|Youngblood]]''\n|\n* Released: 15 June 2018\n* Label: Capitol\n* Format: CD, DL, LP, streaming\n| 1 || 3 || 3 || 7 || 43 || 3 || 2 || 2 || 3 || 1\n|\n* US: 700,000<ref name=\"Youngblood US\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8462423/5-seconds-of-summer-third-no-1-album-billboard-200-chart|title=5 Seconds of Summer Earn Third No. 1 Album on Billboard 200 Chart With 'Youngblood'|website=Billboard|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=24 June 2018|accessdate=25 June 2018}}</ref>\n|\n* ARIA: Gold<ref>{{cite certification|region=Australia|type=album|certyear=2019|accessdate=28 April 2019}}</ref>\n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\" />\n* IFPI DEN: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ifpi.dk/node/8020|title=5 Seconds of Summer \u2013 Youngblood|work=IFPI Denmark|date=12 March 2019|accessdate=19 March 2019}}</ref>\n* MC: Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Calm (album)|Calm]]''\n|\n* Released: 27 March 2020<ref>