illboard.com/music/5-seconds-of-summer/chart-history/hot-100|title=5 Seconds of Summer Song Chart History: Billboard Hot 100|website=Billboard|accessdate=6 March 2018|location=United States}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Out of My Limit\"<ref group=upper-alpha>\"Out of My Limit\" was only released in [[Australia]] and [[New Zealand]].</ref><ref name=\"Out of My Limit iTunes\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/out-of-my-limit-single/1444397805|title=Out of My Limit - Single by 5 Seconds of Summer on Apple Music|publisher=[[iTunes]]|accessdate=5 September 2013}}</ref>\n| 2012\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| ''Somewhere New EP''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[She Looks So Perfect]]\"\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 2014\n| 1 || 20 || 25 || 12 || 40 || 1 || 13 || 1 || 1 || 24\n|\n* ARIA: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA Singles 2014\">{{cite certification|region=Australia|type=single|certyear=2014|accessdate=21 January 2015}}</ref>\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* IFPI DEN: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ifpi.dk/node/5541|title=5 Seconds of Summer \u2013 She Looks So Perfect|work=IFPI Denmark|date=16 July 2014|accessdate=19 March 2019}}</ref>\n* MC: Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n* RMNZ: Platinum<ref>{{cite web | url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=2471 | title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart \u2013 7 April 2014 | publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]] | accessdate=4 July 2014}}</ref>\n* RIAA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite certification |region=United States |artist=5 Seconds of Summer |title=She Looks So Perfect |accessdate=10 September 2015}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''5 Seconds of Summer''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Don't Stop (5 Seconds of Summer song)|Don't Stop]]\"\n| 3 || 16 || 34 || 18 || 63 || 1 || 25 || 1 || 2 || 47   \n|\n* ARIA: Gold<ref name=\"ARIA Singles 2014\"/>\n* BPI: Gold<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* RIAA: Gold<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Amnesia (5 Seconds of Summer song)|Amnes