erful\"<br>{{small|(Major Lazer featuring Ellie Goulding and Tarrus Riley)}}\n| James Slater\n| <ref>{{cite web |last=Kreps |first=Daniel |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-major-lazers-diner-ruining-powerful-video-with-ellie-goulding-20150724 |title=Watch Major Lazer's Diner-Ruining 'Powerful' Video With Ellie Goulding |work=[[Rolling Stone]] |date=24 July 2015 |accessdate=24 July 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"On My Mind\"\n| Emil Nava\n| <ref>{{cite web |last=Strecker |first=Erin |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6700775/ellie-goulding-on-my-mind-video |title=Ellie Goulding Rides a Horse Through a Casino in 'On My Mind' Video |work=Billboard |date=21 September 2015 |accessdate=21 September 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Army\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2016\n| Conor McDonnell\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vevo.com/watch/ellie-goulding/Army/GBUV71600023 |title=Army \u2013 Ellie Goulding |publisher=[[Vevo]] |date=14 January 2016 |accessdate=14 January 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Something in the Way You Move\"\n| Ed Coleman\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vevo.com/watch/ellie-goulding/something-in-the-way-you-move/GBUV71600056 |title=Something In The Way You Move \u2013 Ellie Goulding |publisher=Vevo |date=23 February 2016 |accessdate=23 February 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Still Falling for You\"\n| Emil Nava\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vevo.com/watch/ellie-goulding/Still-Falling-For-You/GBUV71601272 |title=Still Falling For You \u2013 Ellie Goulding |publisher=Vevo |date=25 August 2016 |accessdate=27 August 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"First Time\"<br>{{small|(with Kygo)}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n| [[Mathew Cullen]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |last=Gottlieb |first=Steven |url=https://www.videostatic.com/watch-it/2017/05/23/kygo-ellie-goulding-first-time-mathew-cullen-dir |title=Kygo & Ellie Goulding \"First Time\" (Mathew Cullen, dir.) |publisher=VideoStatic |date=23 May 2017 |accessdate=